title: 6: Female Friendships and Fall Outs
itunes:title: Female Friendships and Fall Outs
itunes:author: The Try Guys & Ramble
itunes:subtitle: We talk about making new friends, and dropping the problem ones.
content:encoded:
In today's episode we talk about female friendships, how to make new friends in your 20's, and how to break up with friends when its just not working out. Also Becky brings an argument to our new segment: Couples Court!
